provenance: Albertina dup. (') no stamp; Colnaghi; Knoedler & Co. 1926. NGA 46; NGA (handbook) 131.
text: Three Cosmic Powers belong to the Tarocchi set: Iliace (Genius of the Sun), Chronico (Genius of Time), and Cosmico (Genius of the World). Cosmico, wearing the wings of a spirit, holds a sphere of the earth.
title: Genius of the World (The Genii and Virtues)
